# Joint time log

**Canonical ledger:** [true-industries-playbook/time-log.json](https://github.com/TrueIndustriesInc/true-industries-playbook/blob/main/time-log.json)

- **Billing:** joint — count our work together, not agent-only.
- **Sibling workspace:** if `../true-industries-playbook/time-log.json` exists, append there directly.
- **Standalone clone:** append to `docs/time-log-queue.json`; the hub daily workflow merges the queue into the canonical ledger.
- **When:** end of each shipping turn, or when the user asks to log time.
- **Minutes:** round to nearest 5; err slightly high on multi-commit sessions.
- **Fields:** `id` (`T-YYYY-MM-DD-###`), `date`, `minutes`, `repos[]`, `category`, `summary`, `source` (`agent` | `manual` | `backfill`). Optional `session`.

```bash
node ../true-industries-playbook/scripts/sum-time.mjs   # when playbook is a sibling
```
